442
00:42:11,679 --> 00:42:23,760
[SPEAKER_00] Ne mogu se sjetiti vremenskog okvira, ali išao sam, nisam bio na WWDC-u 2019., ali sam bio u susjedstvu WWDC-a.

443
00:42:24,559 --> 00:42:29,920
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, bio sam tamo oko San Josea i provodio vrijeme s ljudima.

444
00:42:30,159 --> 00:42:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, definitivno sam htjela nešto objaviti prije toga.

445
00:42:34,320 --> 00:42:34,880
[SPEAKER_00] To ima smisla.

446
00:42:35,039 --> 00:42:36,320
[SPEAKER_00] Tako bih mogla upoznati ljude.

447
00:42:36,320 --> 00:42:42,159
