536
00:51:06,000 --> 00:51:07,039
[SPEAKER_00] Samo su moje ideje dobre.

537
00:51:08,800 --> 00:51:09,360
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, ne, ne.

538
00:51:10,239 --> 00:51:13,920
[SPEAKER_00] Jednostavno želim biti uzbuđen onim na čemu radim.

539
00:51:16,000 --> 00:51:18,480
