554
00:53:32,880 --> 00:53:35,280
[SPEAKER_01] Definitivno je mnogo teže raditi s njom.

555
00:53:35,519 --> 00:53:36,800
[SPEAKER_01] I imao sam stvari na kojima sam radio.

556
00:53:37,039 --> 00:53:39,679
